data.description: Vacant and Ready for you! Welcome to Your new Gorgeous 3 Bed, 2 Bath, Move-in Ready Home in the Highly Desirable Arrowhead Ranch Area. As you step Inside, You'll immediately notice the Vaulted Ceilings and abundant Natural Light. The Living Areas and Kitchen are Adorned with Tile Flooring, Recessed Lighting, and wired Speakers. The Kitchen is a Chef's Delight with Granite Countertops, Stainless Steel appliances, Double Ovens, and a Dry bar with Built-in Wine Fridge. Primary Bedroom Boasts an ensuite Bathroom with Walk-in Shower and Separate Tub. There's a Large Backyard with enough room for a pool. You'll notice the Covered Patio, Storage Shed, and R.V. Gate. Additional Upgrades include a New Roof, Security Screens, Dual Pane Windows, and leased Solar Panels. Easy to Show! See it Today! Shopping, Dining, Parks are all just minutes away. Don't Miss out schedule your showing today! Will get it professionally cleaned before close of escrow.
